sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: User types note into input field

    Note right of browser: User clicks Save

    browser->>browser: Submit event handler triggered
    Note right of browser: event.preventDefault() prevents page reload

    browser->>browser: Create note object\n{ content, date }

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    Note left of server: Server receives JSON\nand stores the new note
    server-->>browser: JSON response (e.g., {"message":"note created"})
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: Promise callback executes

    browser->>browser: Add new note to DOM dynamically
    browser->>browser: Clear input field